markets.title: Will federal **student loan forbearance** be extended again?
markets.expiration_value: The student loan payment pause was extended through August 31, 2022
markets.rules_primary: If there is a release on the websites of the White House or Department of Education, issued between Issuance and May 1, 2022, extending federal student loan forbearance past May 1, 2022, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Please see FORB in the Rulebook for the legally binding terms and conditions, including the rules regarding variable expiration and closure.
